    answer: "22",
    options: ["20", "21", "22", "23"],
    explanation: "Sea x lápices azules. Rojos: 2x. Verdes: 2x-12. Total: x+2x+(2x-12)=98 → 5x-12=98 → 5x=110 → x=22."
