    answer: "600",
    options: ["400", "500", "600", "700"],
    explanation: "Unidades de Y = 25% de 1200 = 300. Sean x, y, z las unidades de X, Y, Z. x+y+z=1200, y=300 → x+z=900 → x=900-z. Ecuación de horas: 2x+3y+5z=4500 → 2(900-z)+3×300+5z=4500 → 1800-2z+900+5z=4500 → 2700+3z=4500 → 3z=1800 → z=600."
